üìò Overview

The SolarEdge Monitoring Server API provides a RESTful interface for accessing SolarEdge‚Äôs cloud-based monitoring platform data.
It enables integration with other systems for data analysis, fleet management, and visualization of site and equipment performance.

API Base URL:

https://monitoringapi.solaredge.com

